    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "a9ceadf4-e36f-4aa8-8571-f72ed6a0ea05",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "fa7771a4-2c1a-44d9-97cc-a693b3a0b810",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "7fbabfd1-bcfe-4d2f-a793-483bb5864b23",
                            "text": "Look at the Sarcophagus",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6c1aed0e-de0d-486b-a15e-d230ff629fa0",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I can't imagine how long it must've taken the Knights Luminar to have this all put here. How much work it must've taken.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "081e2259-563f-495a-94b9-f8da87b8bf58",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Some of the bodies down here are almost certainly workers who died building it. Not in the sarcophagi, though. Those must've gone mostly to the Knights themselves.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "65b049b1-c188-44c2-918e-5e465a089848",
                            "text": "Open the Sarcophagus",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6101836d-a9c6-4b0e-bea2-fc502f74a3e7",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "No doubt there are some trinkets in these that I wouldn't mind accidentally acquiring. I mean, they're not doing anyone any good down here.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "920720cb-7bcb-4abe-af04-be1998179c57",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Those lids, though, are just too much trouble to deal with. I think the <i>right</i> thing to do is to come back sometime with a small raiding party and strip all these things bare. That's the sensible and honorable way to do it.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": "1",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                    "Unique": false
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}